    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this car to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it still looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about keeping it spotless inside and out\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It's been garage-kept and loved every single mile. I'm looking for a quick, easy sale to a good home, so feel free to reach out with any questions. I'm happy to chat! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
