      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and is honestly a total dream to drive. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and looks absolutely flawless, you\u2019ve found it! I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
