    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six and the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is mechanically superlative; the high-revving powerplant benefits from documented rod bearing replacement and a precision-calibrated double VANOS system. The chassis integrity is preserved via a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural rigidity required for the M-variable differential lock to perform as intended. The factory-spec suspension geometry remains tight, providing the tactile feedback and surgical turn-in characteristic of a true analog driver's car. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the exterior maintains its factory-applied clear coat with zero evidence of oxidation or panel gap variance. Every bushing, seal, and fluid interval is current, making this a turn-key acquisition for the uncompromising enthusiast.",
